  #read-the-paper
    .paper-details
        h3
          a(href="http://vis.berkeley.edu/papers/videodigests/") Video Digests: A Browsable, Skimmable Format for Informational Lecture Videos
        p.authors 
          a(href="https://www.amypavel.com") Amy Pavel
          | , 
          a(href="https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~cjrd/") Colorado Reed
          | , 
          a(href="http://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~bjoern/") Bjoern Hartmann
          | , 
          a(href="http://graphics.stanford.edu/~maneesh/") Maneesh Agrawala
        p.conference UIST 2014, October 2014. 
        p
          a(href="https://github.com/ucbvislab/vdigests") Code on GitHub


  #build-vd
    h3 Create a Video Digest
    ol
      li 
        a(href="/signup") Create an account
        |   (contact Amy [apavel at cs dot cmu dot edu] for the beta access code)
      li
        a(href="/editor") Add a YouTube video url, which will bring you to the editor
      li Once finished editing the video digest, you can publish the results and share the link
      li
        a(href="/tutorial") Check out a full tutorial here.
